	<h1 class="title">《星战》背后的特效公司找了个中国股东，不光是因为钱</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/102277/small/102277.jpg?1432868256" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">韩方航 俞斯译</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-12 19:17:22 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20597/medium/20597.jpg?1452582855" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="20597" data-title="《《星战》背后的特效公司找了个中国股东，不光是因为钱》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/20597/medium/20597.jpg?1452582855" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/20597.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
